  <header class="header">
    <a target="_top"><img src="https://blog.flamingtext.com/blog/2020/01/29/flamingtext_com_1580304812_588560751.png" style="padding-top: 75px;" border="0" alt="Logo Design by FlamingText.com" title="Logo Design by FlamingText.com"></a>
